task.summary: Add plot cost training in ClassifierMetrics
It is changed MLP class for MLPClassifier and MLPRegression
It is added base class for Ensemble
It is added ModelCombinator class for combining the output of Ensemble, also some warnings are repaired
It is changed name classes (style PEP8)
It is added basic training for an ensemble
It is added example with MNIST data base. It is changed the locations some files and it is added "MLPModel" as base class for MLP regressor and classifier.
It was completed docstring for all current classes.
Changed how to construct a network, similar to Lasagne and Keras library.
Changed training function of ensemble for compute iternal data of the combiner method. Also it is added Weight Averaging method for output ensembles.
Fixed some sphinx warnings. Added requirements for readthedocs.
Changed conf.py in docs for redirect source code to Github.
Changed absolute imports in each module to relative imports.
Added numpydoc as style docstring for Sphinx documentation.
Added path library libml in requirements file.
Fixed error libml in requirements file.
Changed name main package in setup.py
Changed way to get the package path in conf.py
Test 9 ReadTheDocs. Added License MIT. Changed setup.
Deleted wiki git in PyCharm Proyect.
